{"tid":1075171,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位女朋友 醒路啦","createTime":"2019-03-24T02:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T07:54:20.000Z","uid":205775,"like":93,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f02fe68263141ea0fe2cecb43bc98f001d9ac486","tid":1075171,"uid":205775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"我有兩個男仔fd 佢地都有女朋友 <br />\n其中一個 會有意無意無啦啦無撚端端 同你講曖昧野<br />\n<br />\n另外一個 會等女友訓左 係撚啦啦打電話黎話要 談心<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 有女友就檢點啲啦 <br />\n <br />\n佢地都係人地睇落覺得好仔嘅男人 又話佢專一 話佢忠誠<br />\n我就唔撚信 佢地會將同我講嘅野同佢地自己女朋友講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忠咩撚野誠呀 <br />\n如果我男朋友 趁我瞓咗 打比其他女講心事 / 講曖說話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我一定嬲撚到仆街</span><br />\n所以話冇一個男人唔想出䡄<br />\n只係睇佢 會唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒路啦 各位女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8279de9c6d7f2b57b5c0f1d16f972319c2c2d886","tid":1075171,"uid":185914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇接受人地同你談心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ec34cbbb0717f027a8600b4c3ea1f883be60c4","tid":1075171,"uid":176802,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"有女朋友搵男性朋友傾下計都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線"},{"pid":"efbaef56548b229ad9db893856f4025a16bab944","tid":1075171,"uid":172733,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"邊到鄉下？ 醒咩路"},{"pid":"a3da6426222b9ad52c74a0687de2db8556d7e939","tid":1075171,"uid":7915,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦<br />\n全世界男人都會出軌啦<br />\n滿意未？"},{"pid":"b4807b275490cfd1647833f30639c16fb25dba80","tid":1075171,"uid":7915,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦<br />\n全世界男人